modules.description: Performs topological sorting of tasks with dependencies using Kahn's algorithm. Operates on association lists where each key represents a task and its value is a list of dependent tasks. Handles cyclic dependency detection and returns a sorted list of tasks in dependency order.

Performs topological sorting of directed graphs, including handling of cycles by partitioning into strongly connected components. Processes association lists representing nodes and their dependencies, returning ordered lists or grouped components. Detects missing nodes in dependency lists to identify invalid graph entries.
